Pack up your item as soon as the buyer pays. Find the lightest packaging material as possible to minimize the shipping cost.

Print your discounted shipping label directly from eBay. Enter the dimensions and weight of your packaged item, and choose a shipping service. You can use any printer and regular paper, then tape it to your package.
Drop your package off at the post office or schedule a pickup. Tracking is included when you use our labels so you can see when the item gets delivered.
